				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>The Google IO developer sandbox contains a small easter egg.</p>
<p>They are having some fun with the <strong>DogeCoin meme</strong>.</p>
<p>Navigate to the sandbox page <a href="https://www.google.com/events/io/sandbox">here</a> and scroll down to the &#8220;Put your app out there&#8221; title, then click the tablets screen.</p>
